    <item>
      <title>历史表明，降息对于利润预测来说并不是好消息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/interest-rate-cuts-aren-t-good-news-for-profit-forecasts-history-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经济复苏的推动下，股市与企业利润预期同步上涨。但如果以史为鉴，迫在眉睫的降息可能会改变剧本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/interest-rate-cuts-aren-t-good-news-for-profit-forecasts-history-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 11:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
