    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚通胀创27年来新高，加息迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/nigeria-inflation-rate-climbs-to-27-year-high-on-transport-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于燃料补贴的停止导致运输成本上升以及奈拉贬值，尼日利亚消费者价格在 12 月份以近三十年来最快的速度攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/nigeria-inflation-rate-climbs-to-27-year-high-on-transport-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 11:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>仅 0.001% 的韩国交易中发现“猖獗”的裸短裤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/korea-says-naked-shorts-are-rampant-but-they-make-up-0-001-of-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金融当局将非法裸卖空描述为“猖獗”，他们用这一说法来证明去年 11 月突然禁止在价值 1.8 万亿美元的股票市场上进行所有形式的卖空。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/korea-says-naked-shorts-are-rampant-but-they-make-up-0-001-of-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:14:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
