      <title>消息人士称，宝马的华晨中国合作伙伴考虑出售合资公司股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/bmw-s-brilliance-china-partner-said-to-consider-selling-jv-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，宝马汽车公司在中国的汽车制造合作伙伴的所有者正在考虑筹集资金的方案，包括出售该公司在与这家德国制造商的合资企业中的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-15/bmw-s-brilliance-china-partner-said-to-consider-selling-jv-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 04:36:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东风险与利率前景争夺，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价小幅走低，原因是美国及其盟国针对胡塞武装的空袭将引发更广泛的冲突并扰乱中东的原油流动，而交易员评估货币政策前景时，更广泛的市场基调走软，平衡了这一风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 23:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
